			<action-desc>
        <sponsor name-id="S306">Mr. Menendez</sponsor> (for
			 himself and <cosponsor name-id="S166">Mr. Lautenberg</cosponsor>) introduced
			 the following bill; which was read twice and referred to the
			 <committee-name committee-id="SSBK00">Committee on Banking, Housing, and Urban
			 Affairs</committee-name>
      </action-desc>
